ld structure can be highly altered by a\ncollapse and so measurements from this region alone can give unreliable\nestimates of the initial field configuration before collapse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Nov 2014 17:05:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
