he apparent horizon throughout the evolution of the universe. We also made a\nstatefinder analysis of the model and found that it is distinguishably\ndifferent from the standard $\\Lambda$CDM model at present, but shows a de\nSitter type behavior in the far future of the evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Nov 2014 09:22:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Dec 2014 06:19:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2016 05:34:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-28"}
